der（在-下）+handed（手的）→在下面做手脚→秘密的"},{"type":"entry","text":"shrivel","headword":"shrivel"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. (使)枯签(to draw into wrinkles especially with a loss of moisture)"},{"type":"text","text":"['frrv]"},{"type":"text","text":"mummify, wilt, wither"},{"type":"entry","text":"containment","headword":"containment"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.阻止，退制(keeping sth. within limits)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kan'ternmant]"},{"type":"definition","text":"a policy of containment 制政策"},{"type":"entry","text":"attrition","headword":"attrition"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 摩擦，磨损(the act of wearing or grinding down by friction)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'tr{n]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：at（处于）+trit（摩擦）+ion→摩擦，磨损"},{"type":"entry","text":"reversible","headword":"reversible"},{"type":"definition","text":"adji 可逆的，可反转的(capable of being reversed or of reversing)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'v3:rsab]"},{"type":"entry","text":"pacifist","headword":"pacifist"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.和平主义者，反战主义者（a person who believes that all wars are wrong and"},{"type":"text","text":"['paesrfrst]"},{"type":"text","text":"refuses to fight in them)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：paci(y)（和平）+ist（信仰某种主义的人）→和平主义者"},{"type":"entry","text":"mitigant","headword":"mitigant"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj缓和的，减轻的n.缓和物"},{"type":"text","text":"['mitagant]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自mitigate（v.使缓和，使减轻）"},{"type":"entry","text":"dual","headword":"dual"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 双重的(having or composed of two parts)"},{"type":"text","text":"['du:al]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：du（二，双）+al→两个的→双重的"},{"type":"entry","text":"thousandfold","headword":"thousandfold"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 干倍的(a thousand times as much) adv. 千倍地"},{"type":"text","text":"['auzndfauld]"},{"type":"text","text":"园组合词：thousand（一千）+fold（折叠）→一千个叠起来→千倍的"},{"type":"entry","text":"ignominious","headword":"ignominious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 可耶的(despicable);耶辱的(dishonorable)"},{"type":"text","text":"[igna'mrnias]"},{"type":"text","text":"disgraceful, humiliating"},{"type":"entry","text":"snippet","headword":"snippet"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.小片，片段(a small part, piece, or thing)"},{"type":"text","text":"[sniprt]"},{"type":"text","text":"snippet of information/news 简短的信息/新闻"},{"type":"entry","text":"befriend","headword":"befriend"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 以朋友态度对待(to become or act as a friend to)"},{"type":"text","text":"[br'frend]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：be（使）+friend（朋友）→当作朋友→以朋友态度对待"},{"type":"entry","text":"drastic","headword":"drastic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj猛烈的，激烈的（strong: violent and severe)"},{"type":"text","text":"['draestrk]"},{"type":"definition","text":"a drastic change剧烈的变化"},{"type":"entry","text":"subtract","headword":"subtract"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 减去，减掉(to take away by or as if by deducting)"},{"type":"text","text":"[sab'traekt]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：sub（下面）+tract（拉）→拉下去→减去"},{"type":"entry","text":"huckster","headword":"huckster"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.叫卖小贩，零售商(a peddler or hawker)"},{"type":"text","text":"['hAkstar]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：huck（看作back，背）+ster（人）→背东西卖的人→叫卖小贩"},{"type":"entry","text":"orchestrate","headword":"orchestrate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.给-配管弦乐（to provide with orchestration)：精心安排，组织（to arrange or"},{"type":"text","text":"[':rkistrert]"},{"type":"text","text":"combine so as to achieve a desired or maximum effect)"},{"type":"entry","text":"unpack","headword":"unpack"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 打开包裹(或行李)，卸货(to take packed things out of)"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'paek]"},{"type":"entry","text":"ravage","headword":"ravage"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 推毁,使荒废(to ruin and destroy)"}]},{"number":367,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<< GRE词汇精选 乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"distribute","headword":"distribute"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 分发, 分配(to separate sth. into part and give a share to each person)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'strrbju:t]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：dis（分开）+tribut（给予）+e→分开给→分发"},{"type":"entry","text":"untarnished","headword":"untarnished"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj未失去光泽的（unblemished)"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'ta:rnxjt]"},{"type":"text","text":"stainless, unstained, unsullied, untained"},{"type":"entry","text":"excess","headword":"excess"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 过分，过度(lack of moderation; intemperance)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rk'ses]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：ex（向外）+cess（走）→走出常规→过分"},{"type":"text","text":"Perhaps because he feels confined by an excess of parental restrictions and"},{"type":"text","text":"rules, at adolescence the repressd child may break out dramatically"},{"type":"entry","text":"herbaceous","headword":"herbaceous"},{"type":"text","text":"adlj. 草本的(of, relating to, or having the characteristics of an herb)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：herb（草）+aceous具有-特征的）→草本的"},{"type":"text","text":"[3:r'berfas]"},{"type":"entry","text":"self-realization","headword":"self-realization"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.自我实现，自我完成(fulfilment by oneself of the possibilities of one's character"},{"type":"text","text":"[,self,ri:ala'zerfn]"},{"type":"text","text":"or personality)"},{"type":"entry","text":"penalize","headword":"penalize"},{"type":"definition","text":"v置-于不利地位(to put at a serious disadvantage);处罚(to inflict a penalty on)"},{"type":"text","text":"['pi:nalarz]"},{"type":"text","text":"@来自penal（adj惩罚的，刑罚的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"atonement","headword":"atonement"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 弥(reparation for an offense or injury)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'taunmant]"},{"type":"text","text":"来自atone（v弥补，赎罪）"},{"type":"entry","text":"bibliomania","headword":"bibliomania"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 藏书邮(extreme preoccupation with collecting books)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,brbla'menra]"},{"type":"entry","text":"counterclockwise","headword":"counterclockwise"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj逆时针方向的adv.逆时针方向地"},{"type":"text","text":"[,kauntar'kla:kwaiz]"},{"type":"entry","text":"unpremeditated","headword":"unpremeditated"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj无预谋的，非故意的"},{"type":"text","text":"[Anpri'meditertid]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：un（不）+premeditated（预谋的）→无预谋的"},{"type":"entry","text":"premonition","headword":"premonition"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 预感，预兆(a feeling that sth. is going to happen)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pri:ma'nx{n]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：pre（预先）+monit（警告）+ion→预先给出的警告→预感，预兆"},{"type":"text","text":"foreboding, prenotion, presage, presentiment"},{"type":"entry","text":"provocation","headword":"provocation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.挑蚌，激怒(the act of provoking: incitement)"},{"type":"text","text":"[.pra:va'ker{n]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自provoke（v激怒）"},{"type":"entry","text":"trample","headword":"trample"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 坏，践踏(to tread heavily so as to bruise, crush, or injure);骤踊"},{"type":"text","text":"['trampl]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：tr（看作tree，树）+ample（大量的）→大量的树苗被踩坏→踩坏，践路"},{"type":"entry","text":"urgency","headword":"urgency"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 紧急(的事)(the quality or state of being urgent)"},{"type":"text","text":"['3:rdzansi]"},{"type":"text","text":"importunity, urging"},{"type":"entry","text":"interrelate","headword":"interrelate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.相互关联，相互影响(to bring into mutual relation;have mutual relationship)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ntarr'lert]"}]},{"number":368,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 33 >>)"},{"type":"entry","text":"packed","headword":"packed"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj压紧的，压实的(compressed）：充满人的，拥挤的（crowded,crammed)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pakt]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自pack（v打包，包装）"},{"type":"entry","text":"sight","headword":"sight"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.景象(spectacle);视力(the process, power, or function of seeing);视野(the"},{"type":"text","text":"[sart]"},{"type":"text","text":"range of vision) v. 看到(to get or catch sight of)"},{"type":"t