. 香料(any of various aromatic vegetable products) v 给调味(to add spice to"},{"type":"text","text":"[spars]"},{"type":"text","text":"food in order to give it more flavor)"},{"type":"entry","text":"sculptural","headword":"sculptural"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 雕刻的(of or relating to sculpture);雕刻般的"},{"type":"text","text":"['skAlpt[aral]"},{"type":"text","text":"sculptural arts雕塑艺术"},{"type":"entry","text":"dorsal","headword":"dorsal"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj背部的，背脊的(of, on, or near the back)"},{"type":"text","text":"[d:rsl]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：dors（背）+al→背部的"},{"type":"entry","text":"untamed","headword":"untamed"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 未服的(not controlled by anyone)"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'termd]"},{"type":"entry","text":"negligibly","headword":"negligibly"},{"type":"definition","text":"adv.无足轻重地，不值一提地"},{"type":"text","text":"['neglidzabli]"},{"type":"text","text":"国来自negligible（adj.可以忽略的，微不足道的）"}]},{"number":369,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"unpalatable","headword":"unpalatable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj味道差的，不好吃的（not palatable;unpleasant to taste）：令人不快的"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'palatabl]"},{"type":"text","text":"(unpleasant and difficult for the mind to accept)"},{"type":"text","text":"过联想记忆：un（不）+palatable（合意的）→令人不快的"},{"type":"text","text":"Animals that have tasted unpa/atable plants tend to recognize them afterward"},{"type":"text","text":"on the basis of their most conspicuous features, such as their flowers."},{"type":"entry","text":"reciprocation","headword":"reciprocation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 互换(a mutual exchange);报答(a return in kind or of like value)：往复运动(an"},{"type":"text","text":"[ri,sipra'ker{n]"},{"type":"text","text":"alternating motion)"},{"type":"text","text":"reciprocation of ---的回报"},{"type":"entry","text":"crimson","headword":"crimson"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 绑红色(any of several deep purplish reds) adj. 绑红色的(of the color crimson)"},{"type":"text","text":"[krmzn]"},{"type":