covered that mitochondria and chloroplasts share a"},{"type":"text","text":"long, identifiable sequence of DNA:; such a coincidence could be explained only"},{"type":"text","text":"by the transfer of DNA between the two systems."}]},{"number":371,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"underrepresented","headword":"underrepresented"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj未被充分代表的(inadequatelyrepresented)"},{"type":"text","text":"[Anda,reprr'zentid]"},{"type":"text","text":"Despite the growing prominence of Hispanic actors in the American"},{"type":"text","text":"theater, many Hispanic experts feel that the Spanish-speaking population is"},{"type":"text","text":"unclerrepresentec on the stage."},{"type":"entry","text":"bastion","headword":"bastion"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 堡垒，防御工事(a projecting part of a fortification)"},{"type":"text","text":"[bastian]"},{"type":"entry","text":"flaunt","headword":"flaunt"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 炫羅,夸趣 (to display or obtrude oneself to public notice)"},{"type":"text","text":"[flo:nt]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆联想记忆：fl（看作fly，飞）+aunt（姑姑）→姑姑到处飞→炫耀"},{"type":"text","text":"Fortunately. she was deprecatory about her"},{"type":"text","text":"hover"},{"type":"text","text":"accomplishments, properly unwilling to flaunr them"},{"type":"text","text":"before her friends."},{"type":"text","text":"flash, parade, show off"},{"type":"entry","text":"hover","headword":"hover"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 翔(to remain fluttering in the air); (人)得徊(to linger"},{"type":"text","text":"['hAvar]"},{"type":"text","text":"near a place)"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：爱人（lover）在自己身边徘徊（hover）"},{"type":"entry","text":"congruity","headword":"congruity"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.一致性，适合性（the quality or state of being congruent or congruous)：共同点"},{"type":"text","text":"[kan'grurti]"},{"type":"text","text":"(a point of agreement)"},{"type":"entry","text":"criss-cross","headword":"criss-cross"},{"type":"definition","t